Insight Global is a premier IT services firm with 41 locations in the US and Canada. Insight Global provides contract services to Federal and Commercial Customers  in IT, Accounting, Finance, and Engineering. Insight Global employs over 26,000 people  each year with revenues over $1.4 Billion. Insight Global’s focus on client relationships and rapid response times generates unmatched client satisfaction.Our greatest asset is our people, who are committed to open, frequent communication with our clients and our consultants. It is our ability to develop these professional and personal relationships that has led to our rapid growth.
